PN,38201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FMajor changes to Jersey's healthcare
OL,7,Fsystem will see adult patients charged
OL,8,F#502 for each day they stay in
OL,9,Fhospital unnecessarily.
OL,11,FThe island's Health Minister, Deputy
OL,12,FTom Binet, says the fees are being
OL,13,Fintroduced to free up capacity,
OL,14,Fstating that approximately 1,000 'bed
OL,15,Fdays' are lost to such patients each
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FHe explains these delays "prevent
OL,19,Fothers from being admitted and
OL,20,Freceiving the care they need".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FThe new charges will be brought in
OL,7,Fimmediately with some caveats: a
OL,8,Fsuitable care package at home or in
OL,9,Fanother setting must be provided, and
OL,10,Fthe fees will only apply five working
OL,11,Fdays after the patient is due to leave
OL,12,Ffollowing the end of their hospital
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FThose "experiencing mental health
OL,16,Fdifficulties, who lack capacity, who
OL,17,Fhave exceptional personal
OL,18,Fcircumstances or where there are
OL,19,Fsafety concerns" are exempt.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FDeputy Binet adds: "We're not seeking
OL,7,Fto penalise people or generate
OL,8,Ffunding, we just want to ensure that
OL,9,Fhospital beds are only occupied by
OL,10,Fpatients who need hospital care and
OL,11,Ffree up space to treat more patients."
OL,13,FVisitors to Jersey will also have to
OL,14,Fpay for emergency treatment from
OL,15,FMonday 13 April, unless they are
OL,16,Fcovered under a reciprocal agreement
OL,17,Fwhich allows Jersey residents to
OL,18,Freceive free healthcare when
OL,19,Ftravelling to those countries.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FPlaces such as the UK, France and
OL,7,FPortugal already have deals in place,
OL,8,Fso visitors from these countries will
OL,9,Fnot be affected and can continue to
OL,10,Fclaim it at no charge.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the rule changes will see
OL,13,Fpeople on Jersey work permits given
OL,14,Fstronger healthcare rights from the
OL,15,Fsame date.
OL,17,FThose employed locally will be able to
OL,18,Faccess free ongoing care following
OL,19,Femergency treatment on island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FDeputy Binet explains: "As healthcare
OL,7,Fcosts continue to rise faster than
OL,8,Finflation, we must ensure that we make
OL,9,Fthe best use of the fixed resources we
OL,10,Fhave, as well as treating people
OL,11,Ffairly.
OL,13,F"This includes recognising that work
OL,14,Fpermit holders are actively
OL,15,Fcontributing to the island's economy
OL,16,Ffor all our benefits, whilst making it
OL,17,Fclear that visitors from countries
OL,18,Fwithout a reciprocal health agreement
OL,19,Fshould have travel insurance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,F"Our current policy of providing free
OL,7,Femergency care to all visitors means
OL,8,Fthat, even when they have travel
OL,9,Finsurance, they can't claim on that
OL,10,Finsurance for the emergency care
OL,11,Fprovided because our policy is it's
OL,12,Ffree.
OL,14,F"In making these changes, we won't
OL,15,Fleave people at risk. Our first course
OL,16,Fof action will always be to provide
OL,17,Fthe emergency care people need. A
OL,18,F'provide and then charge' approach,
OL,19,Fnot 'charge and then provide'."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774897908
OL,3,CPatients to be charged #500 a day if
OL,4,Cthey refuse to leave hospital
OL,6,FThe changes form part of Health and
OL,7,FCare Jersey's plan to focus resources
OL,8,Fon "residents and workers who make a
OL,9,Fsocial or financial contribution to
OL,10,Four island".
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
